name: <collections::vec_deque::drain::Drain<'_, T, A> as core::fmt::Debug>::fmt
src:
fn fmt(&self, f: &mut fmt::Formatter<'_>) -> fmt::Result {
        f.debug_tuple("Drain")
            .field(&self.drain_len)
            .field(&self.idx)
            .field(&self.new_len)
            .field(&self.remaining)
            .finish()
    }
